# When Systems Proceed Under Uncertainty

This repository contains a short, non-prescriptive reference documenting a recurring system-level pattern observed across shared and transitional device contexts.

The pattern concerns situations in which systems proceed—rendering interfaces, previews, notifications, or resumed sessions—before user intent or authority has been resolved.

This material is provided for informational purposes only. It does not propose solutions, recommendations, standards, or evaluations of correctness or responsibility.
